le linkedin select page  systematic investing current openings send us a note cubist systematic strategies our systematic investing business deploys systematic computerdriven trading strategies across multiple liquid asset classes including equities futures and foreign exchange the core of our effort is rigorous research into a wide range of market anomalies fueled by our unparalleled access to a wide range of publicly available data sources the organization is structured to strongly support investment professionals in their research efforts what we look for creative and innovative investment professionals seasoned experts and advanced degree holders ms or phd in finance computer science mathematics physics operations research statistics or other quantitative disciplines strong analytical and quantitative skills with the ability to conduct independent research utilizing large data sets experienced developers with a history of researching or implementing quantitative models for equities futures andor fx either at a firm or independently programming experience in any of the following c java c matlab r q python or perl   note to recruiters if you are a recruiter interested in working with us please send us an email current positions position location research analyst new york data analyst singapore python developer new york point quantitative risk analyst new yorkstamford quantitative developer – high frequency new york quantitative researcher – intern new york point quantitative researcher – big data  machine learning specialist new yorkstamford quantitative researcher – systematic options new york quantitative developer – systematic options new york data scientist new york singapore machine learning researcher – intern new york london quantitative software developer – core java new york machine learning researcher new york london quantitative researcher new york london paris hong kong quantitative portfolio manager new york london paris hong kong ross garon  point asset management facebook twitter google linkedin select page leadership return to leadership ross garon ross garon is a managing director at point asset management lp and the head of cubist systematic strategies llc the firm’s quant business before point mr garon was the cofounder and managing member of tykhe capital llc he began his career in quantitative finance at d e shaw  co in new york london and tokyo  he  also served as head of global business management at commerzbank’s equities division mr garon graduated magna cum laude from harvard university he serves on the boards of neighborhood trust and the andrew goodman foundation the steering committee of itbb and the editorial board of the journal of investment strategies microsoft personalized ad preferences to opt out of personalized ads in this browser your browser history must allow firstparty and thirdparty cookies and you must have your browsing experience set to not delete browsing history on exit instructions for enabling cookies and configuring your browsing history may be available in your browsers settings privacy or help documentation sign in hold on… we’re sorry but this didn’t work you can’t turn off personalized ads right now because your browser is currently blocking thirdparty cookies we can help you fix this issue let’s get started depending on what browser you use open options or settings make sure that thirdparty cookies are not blocked anymore to find out how search your browser’s help revisit httpchoicemicrosoftcomoptout and then on the “personalized ads in this browser” tile click off ext740 about our ads to create a more customized online experience some of the ads you may receive on microsoft websites and apps are tailored to your previous activities searches and site visits youre in control and heres where you can make the advertising choice thats right for you ext where can i learn more about advertising on microsoft websites and apps microsoft partners with oath appnexus and other thir